item.title: CVE-2020-6201|2024-08-04T08:55:22.115Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20commerce%20cloud%20%28testweb%20extension%29
item.description: The SAP Commerce (Testweb Extension), versions- 6.6, 6.7, 1808, 1811, 1905, does not sufficiently encode user-controlled inputs, due to which certain GET URL parameters are reflected in the HTTP responses without escaping/sanitization, leading to Reflected Cross Site Scripting.
